        {
            "title": "AWARD-WINNING || Mobietrain - Creating a Micro-learning Platform || 2017 - 2019",
            "date": {
                "start": {
                    "month": null,
                    "day": null,
                    "year": 2017
                },
                "end": {
                    "month": null,
                    "day": null,
                    "year": 2019
                }
            },
            "description": "How do you make an award-winning micro-learning? From beginning to end, we have guided start-up Mobietrain to develop a new, powerful learning platform for wonderful clients like BMW and Albert Heijn. \n\nWe created a smooth, motivating experience leaning on intrinsic motivation for long-term use. I was able to leverage the power of gamification with a focus on self-improvement and mastery instead of points. Next to creating the reward system and the UX, I helped to create the various learning formats. I also translated their content to micro-learning questions and videos, and helped them out with some voice-over work for the animations. \n\nOur effort was a part of the puzzle that helped Mobietrain win the HR Tech Solution of the Year Award 2019. \n\nAfter the 1st phase, we helped Mobietrain to take the next step. I analysed the current strengths of their experience, spotted opportunities for improvement, create new learning formats and wrote a plan to take the UX and gamification to a higher level. ",
